text: ['3.3.2  Export taxes, charges, levies and quotas', '3.81.  There  are  no  export  taxes,  charges,  or  levies  applied  by  the  Government  or  other  public authorities in the Republic of Moldova.', '3.82.  On 1 January 2014, the export of Moldavian wine to the EU was liberalized.55']
